p.k: Gerry has to face up to some skeletons in his own closet and goes AWOL to discover the truth when his old DCI's body is found in a basement, untouched for 30 years. Last Man Standing Part 1 UK (2015). Cast: Denis Lawson, Dennis Waterman, Nicholas Lyndhurst, Tamzin Outhwaite. Director: Daikin Marsh.
